body:

To be precise what I did, I used `@dependabot` to upgrade dependencies for my project and following pull-requests were offered to me

https://github.com/bonsaiilabs/gatsby-material-ui-storybook-starter/pulls?q=is%3Apr+is%3Aclosed

After downgrading 
```
 gatsby-plugin-sharp: ^2.2.12 => 2.2.16 
```
